<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08080</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : THE OMNIBUS INVESTMENT CODE OF THE PHILIPPINES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to establish a market-responsive, globally competitive, stable, transparent, time-bound and performance-based investment regime and integrated investment promotion programs and strategies. 
Addresses the regulation of investments and administration of incentives and promotion and facilitation functions required of the established and existing Investment Promotion Agencies.
</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “The Omnibus Investment Code of the Philippines.”</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BIRON, FERJENEL G. M.D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-08-09</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-10-08)</td><td>2. Bravo (M.) (000 2018-11-21)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON TRADE AND INDUSTRY ON 2018-08-14</td></tr></table>